<h2>3 · Spot + Fix the Bugs 🐛</h2>
<p><strong>Bug A</strong> — The agent should place blocks across the layer, <strong>then</strong> move up. It moves up too early.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">agent.place(BLOCK)
agent.move(UP, 1)
agent.place(BLOCK)
agent.place(BLOCK)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Fixed code:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

