<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Bug B</strong> — Place a block when on the <strong>bottom layer</strong> <code>OR</code> on an <strong>outer wall</strong>. It only checks the bottom.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">if on_bottom_layer:
    agent.place(BLOCK)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> add the wall check with <code>or</code>.</p>
<p><strong>Fixed code:</strong></p>
