<p><strong>Bug C</strong> — To climb out, break the block above <strong>first</strong>, then move up. Right now it moves up into solid block and gets stuck.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">agent.move(UP, 1)
agent.destroy(UP)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Hint:</strong> make the hole, then move into it.</p>
